user.biography:
I make cakes that don’t look like cakes. 
👩🏽‍🍳 Take my FREE baking course 👇🏽
🍰 Check out @howtocakeit LIVE tutorials
📚 Join my (bake)book club 👇🏽
user.full_name: Epic Cakes - How To Cake It

node.text: With borders slowly starting to reopen around the world, I think it's safe to say that travelling is on the forefront of a lot of our minds 🤔 Take these cakes as inspiration for your next potential travel destination, I know the sushi cake is deeefinitely calling my name 😋

node.text:
I wish the smell of Cinnamon Rolls baking in the oven could be my alarm clock every morning 🤤 These flaky, buttery rolls are a surefire wake up call for anyone in your household so make sure you save the recipe to try this weekend or whenever the craving hits you! 

Find the full recipe here 👉 http://bit.ly/YOsCinnamonRollsRecipe

node.text:
This is why I ♥️ CAKE and all of the talented Bakers in our HowToCakeIt family 🤗
There are so many possibilities when it comes to the type of batter, decorations and overall style, the sky's the limit! 

Here we have:
• Joise's incredible Terrazzo Tile Flower Vase Cake with Nutella Chocolate Cake and Cookie Dough Filling
• Susanne's Novelty Chiffon Sushi Cake 
• Chelsey's gorgeous Vanilla Drip Cake

Comment down below which of the cakes is more your style! 🍰

node.text:
Holy sweettooth I may have gone a little overboard on the sugar here with the Candy Cakes 🤭

I just couldn't decide which candies I wanted to cake up so I settled on making three of my favorites, the Swedish Berry, Watermelon Slice and the classic Peppermint Swirl 👌🏼

Comment down below which is your favorite candy!

node.text: With borders slowly starting to reopen around the world, I think it's safe to say that travelling is on the forefront of a lot of our minds 🤔 Take these cakes as inspiration for your next potential travel destination, I know the sushi cake is deeefinitely calling my name 😋

Joel McHale, one of the funniest people I’ve ever met. So funny in fact that it seems to have rubbed off on Curtis Stone 😂 
I cannot believe the Semi-Finals of @crimescenekitchen are happening TONIGHT 😱 Episode 8 airs at 9PM EST on Fox so set your alarms people and I’ll see you there 👀

node.text:
I wish the smell of Cinnamon Rolls baking in the oven could be my alarm clock every morning 🤤 These flaky, buttery rolls are a surefire wake up call for anyone in your household so make sure you save the recipe to try this weekend or whenever the craving hits you! 

Find the full recipe here 👉 http://bit.ly/YOsCinnamonRollsRecipe

node.text:
BTS Mascot Mini Cakes! 

Making this little BTS army sure wasn't an easy feat but man did they taste good! While they may look mini this actually took 7.5lbs of my Ultimate Chocolate Cake and copious amounts of my Italian Meringue Buttercream to make 😱

Comment down below which one is your FAVE 🤗

node.text:
Hands up if you think Checkerboard Cakes are suuuper aesthetically pleasing 🙋🏽‍♀️

Swipe through to see the process I used to make this bright and fun checkerboard cake!
I started with 7" cake pans as my base and then used my 6" and 3" cutters to cut out smaller circles of cake that would fit snugly inside each other. 

This can be a bit tricky if you're not paying attention to the orders of the colors but just take it slowly and you'll have yourself a showstopper in no time 🤗

Comment down below if you've tried making a Checkerboard Cake before!
